# Sales Performance Dashboard (Power BI)

## Overview
This project presents an end-to-end Sales Performance Dashboard built in Power BI to analyse revenue, profit, and sales trends, and to identify key performance drivers that support business decision-making.

## Tools Used
- Power BI Desktop
- Power Query
- DAX (basic measures)
- Excel

## Dataset
Advance_Sales_Data.xlsx â€” publicly generated sales dataset containing customer, product, regional, and time-based information. No personal or confidential data was used.

## Key Features
- KPI reporting (Total Sales, Total Profit, Total Quantity, Average Order Value)
- Sales, profit, and quantity trends over time
- Category and product performance analysis
- Interactive slicers for region, segment, and year

## Key Insights
- Technology is the highest-performing category by total sales
- Sales and profit fluctuate over time, with stronger performance in later periods
- A small number of products contribute a large share of overall revenue

